Install:
==
  gem install bundler
  bundle install
    
  For captcha:
  == 
    sudo apt-get install imagemagick --fix-missing 

Deployment note:
===
1. Open Procfile file and change the full path of the *.sh file to the correct project location

2. Open foreman/*.conf and change app folder location

3. Copy these .conf files to /etc/init directory
   sudo mv foreman/* /etc/init

4. Start clockwork and delayed job
   sudo start hiringapp

5. Stop clockwork and delayed job   
   sudo stop hiringapp
